{
  "stem": "1975.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 71.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they did is, they built a bridge, protected bridge, whereby they could communicate-- a small ghetto, was called a 'small section'-- when they have to go cross over the-- like a crossover bridge, you know?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there-- there was the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day they just came and they stopped the crossover.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They surrounded the hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They locked in the doctors and-- and everybody else there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put gasoline and they burned everybody alive there, in that-- in that hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The sick and the doctors and nurses, everybody else, they went up in smoke.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they took this part of the ghetto-- they cancelled this overpass, and they just gave that back to the Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, little by little, they start-- the ghetto start shrinking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had also some factories inside the ghetto, where people used to work and fix uniforms and had a-- a shoe repair and uniforms and all kind of-- all kind of repairs for the German-- for the German army people.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's-- later on, I started work in this factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was very good to me, because I was able to-- to steal some marmalade and sugar and some other thing, bring the-- bring into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, this way, we-- I was able-- we were able to survive, because the meager ration that they gave us, I mean, this was just absolutely impossible to-- to-- to live on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that something terrible happened to all the small cities.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
